%h1 Upload Files

%p
  Select a file using the form below, then click "Upload" to upload it. Once the upload is complete,
  you'll be able to copy & paste a link to the file into wiki articles. See 
  %a{:href=>'/WikiHelp'} WikiHelp
  for more information.
  
%form{:action => '/upload', :method => 'post', :enctype => 'multipart/form-data', :id => 'upload_form'}
  %fieldset
    %legend Select a File
    %input{:type => 'file', :name => 'data', :id => 'data'}
    %button{:id => 'submit', :type => 'submit'} Upload
  %div{:class => 'loading', :style => 'display:none;'}
    %img{:src => '/images/loading_small.gif'}
    %em{:style => 'line-height:38px;vertical-align:top;'} Working...
  %div{:class => 'upload_info', :style => 'display:none;'}
  